tip.text: Visitors can take in a panoramic view of the city from the N Seoul Tower Observatory. Perched upon the highest point of Mt. Namsan, this place offers an outstanding view of Seoul.
This place exhibits the history of Seoul from past to present through the use of teddy bears. All teddy bears are posed in scenes recreating historic events as well as various aspects of Seoul life.
